data.description: Home on the market for the first time, original owner. This house has a great layout with a ton of space on a dead end cul-de-sac street. Very large living and family rooms. Well laid out kitchen with a breakfast bar & room for a table to enjoy family meals. Nice sized dining room with a bay window that overlooks the backyard. Master and 2 more large bedrooms upstairs. Master bath has a separate shower and soaking tub along with a walk in closet. Finished 700 square foot basement was just completed. Basement has a very large gathering space and possible 5th bedroom. Backyard has an outbuilding/shed and a creek. New water heater, HVAC was replaced Dec. 2021 and roof is only 3 years old. You'll definitely want to check this one out and make it your future home.
